      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Try it\n\n1) Click the **play** button on the Script node.\n2) Toggle **Result** to see the raw JSON.\n3) The Field node should also update via the edge.\n\nEdit the Script node via the edit drawer to change `data.source`."
      }
